1.clone this repo at the same level where sdk and build directories exists
2.create src folder and copy sampletts.c ttsdemo.c file in the src folder
3.create inc folder copy tplf_tts.h in the inc folder 
4.Copy toolchain folder from https://github.com/BuddyTV/cma-based-media-player/
4.copy EnvSetup.sh(which installs toolchains and vs_build directories) inside newly gloned(TTS_VS) directory
5.Run EnvSetup.sh which will create toolchains folder and vs_build folder 
6.copy Make file  and run make

NOTE:
Before executing binary in VS TV, run below command, 
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/system/bin/chromium:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
